=head1 DESCRIPTION

This provide a streamlined view of the relationships between
engagements and resources. These summaries offer a crucial link between
collaborative engagements and the specific resources involved, such as
opportunities.These summaries are particularly valuable for partners
navigating complex engagements with multiple resources. They enable
quick insights into resource distribution across engagements, support
efficient resource management, and help maintain a clear overview of
collaborative activities.

